{"id": "1445026302393450506", "channel_id": "1445026206507597935", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "**V2.4.0.8 Online Maintenance Announcement**\n\nDear Keeper,\nThe Mythag Administration Office will conduct campus facility maintenance on December 1 at 20:15(UTC+8) . You will be notified once the update is complete and you can re-enter the game. As an apology for any inconvenience caused by the update, we will provide a supply package. Wishing everyone a successful investigation!\n \n[Compensation]\nOnline Maintenance Compensation: Silver×50\n \n[Claim Conditions]\nThe claiming time ends on December 15, 2025 at 23:59. Please remember to go to your mailox in time to claim the supply materials.\n \n[Update Content]\n1. Localization\n[English]\n● The descriptions related to the \"Mr. Wax Figure\" murder case in Chapter 2 of \"Investigation - Faded Legacy\" and the dialogue of the \"Screeching Monster\" in Chapter 3 have been adjusted to make the storyline more coherent.\n● The wording in the Silver communication text messages between \"William\" and \"Wanda\" has been adjusted in two places for smoother and more understandable dialogue.\n● Adjusted unnatural translation wording in 10 skills and Wheel of Destiny effects to make the descriptions more readable and aesthetically pleasing.\n● The Arithmetica cost notation text for derived cards has been shortened for a more aesthetically pleasing interface.\n● The labeling wording in the chapter selection interface of \"Investigation Operation\" has been adjusted. The chapters are now clearly marked as Faded Legacy and Astral Reign, making it easier to understand.\n\n2. Problem Fix\n[Event]\n● Fixed the issue where ranking data display anomalies could occur in the event \"Rebattle the Origin.\"\n● Fixed the issue where the personal ranking in the event \"Rebattle the Origin\" was incorrectly displayed as \"Not Ranked.\"\n● Fixed the issue where the event \"Rebattle Origin\" had an incorrect event name in the rules description for \"Has received level correction\" in the team formation interface\n \n[Normal]\n● Fixed the issue of incorrect gender reference for female Keepers using Lily in the storyline of \"Investigation Operation\" Chapter 3.\n● Fixed the issue where clicking the stacking and strengthening buttons in the \"Inventory\" interface would respond to dismantling.\n● Fixed the issue where the \"Archive Progress\" of the other Keeper would display as the user's own Archive progress when viewing other Keepers' profiles.\n● Fixed the issue where the audio setting \"Mute/Continue Playing when the game interface is not the current window\" failed to take effect and may cause audio playback errors while playing on PC", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T12:18:37.781000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445026206507597935", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0.8 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1445026324854083688", "channel_id": "1445026206507597935", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "In the English Language:\n● Fixed 15 spelling errors across Chapters 2, 3, 6, and 7 of Main Story - Faded Legacy.\n● Revised the description of the \"Mr. Wax\" murder case (Chapter 2) and the translation of the \"Screeching Monster\" lines (Chapter 3) for greater clarity and story coherence.\n● Adjusted communicator dialogue wording in two instances with William and Wanda to improve smoothness.\n● Fixed the spelling errors for the enemy monster \"Surgeon\" and character \"Aeon of Rapture\" in Chapter 8's Resonance descriptions.\n● Revised the translation of \"Rogers Wax Museum\" (Chapter 2) to align with the sign text in the background art.\n● Corrected the state \"Fortress,\" which was incorrectly translated as Reinforced in 4 instances.\n● Corrected the effect description for \"Putney Morning Post+\": it should state that Arithmetica is gained after gaining Counter for the first time each turn.\n● Fixed the Leap effect translation for Awakener Tinct's Defense card; it should state that Leap lets her gain Aliemus one more time.\n● Adjusted the unnatural translation wording in 10 instances of Skills and Wheel of Destiny effects for improved readability.\n● Fixed the machine translation issue in the \"Phantasmal Dive\" text on the Enhanced Awakener interface.\n● Shortened the Arithmetica Cost labeling text for derived cards to make the interface more readable.\n● Adjusted the labeling wording on the Chapter Selection interface. The chapters are now clearly divided into Faded Legacy and Astral Reign.", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T12:18:43.136000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445026206507597935", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0.8 在线维护公告", "forum_channe