{"id": "1445123086415433861", "channel_id": "1445026206507597935", "type": 0, "author_id": "178332860464234498", "author_name": "raumbobulus", "author_bot": false, "content": "Just my 2 cents, but I feel like an event structure where the community has to essentially fight over resources already feels pretty rough, for now it just feels like newer players get left behind and veterans feel pressured to grind as quickly and as much as they can. Just as a suggestion, I would much prefer an event where the community is collectively rewarded for beating a huge raid boss/ altogether dealing a certain threshold of damage, and maybe those who contributed the most damage get extra rewards.", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T18:43:12.890000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-01T18:43:35.753000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445026206507597935", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0.8 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1445123545612161237", "channel_id": "1445026206507597935", "type": 0, "author_id": "178332860464234498", "author_name": "raumbobulus", "author_bot": false, "content": "IMO it would encourage everyone to participate and grind without feeling like they’re missing out otherwise, still keep the exciting limited event feel, and also be rewarding to all levels of players", "timestamp": "2025-12-01T18:45:02.371000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445026206507597935", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0.8 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
